/*
 * Xiao BLE uses the Titan8000 custom kscan driver.
 *
 * Interrupt-driven scanning is intentionally disabled for now.
 * When `interrupt-gpios` is present, the driver switches to interrupt mode and
 * stops polling while idle. If the chosen interrupt line is not reliably wired
 * to key activity, the matrix will appear to “not work” after boot.
 */
&kscan0 {
	wakeup-source;
};
